name: START HERE
description:
Hello All!

When ordering for the Naches School please do the following during check out..

Before submitting payment there will be a clickable link "NOTES TO SELLER", here please let us know where you would like the shirt delivered (Primary School, Intermediate, Middle, High School, ect..) and the name of your Student if you are not an employee at the school. This will ensure your orders get to the right location and to the person who will be at that location during the day.

Please choose ECONOMY shipping this will not charge you for shipping and let's us know that it will be going with the bulk of the orders. If you choose STORE PICK-UP the apparel will be left here and if you choose GROUND this will charge for ground shipping to your desired address.

If at anytime you have questions please call us (509) 453-9950!

Thank you! Yakima Sports Supply

name: BEFORE YOU ORDER, YOU SHOULD KNOW...
description: Hello all, If you were wondering.... (1) We do not have any products on hand, they are all made on a per order basis and can take any where from 1 hour to 1-2 weeks to make your product depending on amount of club orders we are getting. Once your order is completed, it will be here at our Store Front, until a delivery or shipment has been made. (2) Economy Shipping does not deliver or ship unless there is a total value of $200 waiting to be moved. (3) Ground shipping, as soon as your product has been made we will ship it out. (4) Names and numbers, when finishing the checkout process on the paypal page, there is a section where you can add notes to seller. Include your name and number requests there. (5) We do bulk orders. Contact us directly if you are wanting to place a bulk order and we typically can give you better pricing. (6) If you are ordering for a student, please list their name in the notes to seller option. Thank you for your time, Yakima Sports Supply
